{"tid":195204,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"百彈齋主：熱城網絡支持者 同 獨派，民族論者的分別","createTime":"2017-04-10T12:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T10:26:12.000Z","uid":319,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de6a51ab965772217dc571798efa62029d9f7ea6","tid":195204,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T12:39:28.000Z","msg":"話說，台灣時代力量林昶佐，和青政二人會面，然後引起大量城親城邦的人，去「導正」林昶佐，指他們不是獨派，港共扶持，他們和泛民一樣，甚至有人私下：台灣就是這種低水平。<br />\n<br />\n其實一路以來，我們常說熱城網絡攻擊，係香港來說算最熱烈，我看到熱城網絡支持者，有以下的共同點：<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n：絕對的單一政治傾向<br />\n：認定所有非其政治主張者為廢話，無參考價值<br />\n：不介意因政見而無其他朋友及社交<br />\n：在網絡只吸收單一資訊和評論<br />\n：排斥其他思想<br />\n：以特定人物為重心，奉其言行為指向<br />\n：不會批判領袖言行，尊崇政治領袖<br />\n：喜愛群體單一行動</span><br />\n<br />\n當然以上，係好係壞，就自行判斷，但肯定的事，他們上下，好希望定義「只有「『我們才是香港人』」所以，先出現清黨，清算等等，因為他們眼中，政治只有「城邦論」才是唯一正途。<br />\n<br />\n對比之下，他們喜好攻擊的獨派，民族論者，或非我族類就有以下，網絡共同點<span style=\"color: red;\">：<br />\n<br />\n：無政治或人物作重心<br />\n：包容度高（由港奴左膠到城邦）<br />\n：言論力量分散<br />\n：資料方向廣泛而多方向<br />\n：不擅網絡攻勢，網絡動員慢而不集中<br />\n：無指導性的政治傾向<br />\n：敵意動作較少</span><br />\n<br />\n零碎，分散就係獨派，民族論者，脫中解殖人士的特色，對比熱城他們，他們有十數個專頁，死人，KOL，每次面對特定人事，其槍口整齊度，可以講係全港最高，無論係主動開火，還是被動還擊。在政治鬥爭來說，他們有一套組織，所以行事有錯也好，但因為係自己人，都會維護。<br />\n<br />\n相反獨派，民族論者，脫中解殖人士，一大派「無組織」者，就不會因一人或一派之言，而「相信」或聽從行事，每個人，和派之間的獨立性高，就是他們特點，但同時組織鬆散，又是一個現實。<br />\n<br />\n到底那個模式好？我不敢判斷，只能分享我的心得：<br />\n尊敬而不愚忠，響應而不盲從<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CriticsHK/posts/1923167651229679\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCriticsHK%2Fposts%2F1923167651229679&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=6867fa26\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CriticsHK/posts/1923167651229679</a>"},{"pid":"a874b18667c3a9a22b73752847896fc09db5fec5","tid":195204,"uid":4874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T12:43:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/10/204300_59eefcd1dcfdf57ca8b41b0eaa99f9a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F10%2F204300_59eefcd1dcfdf57ca8b41b0eaa99f9a3.jpg&h=c5970c4a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee236f1f7e278a78da63452a66829c4f297dcb05","tid":195204,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T12:45:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/10/204300_59eefcd1dcfdf57ca8b41b0eaa99f9a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F10%2F204300_59eefcd1dcfdf57ca8b41b0eaa99f9a3.jpg&h=c5970c4a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d02df505330b21c95b958fbf2d8fb1a5a86780","tid":195204,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:12:25.000Z","msg":"其實青山教係玩分身<br />\n<br />\n一人整十數個專頁, 扮多人<br />\n<br />\n事實係連街站都開唔到一個"},{"pid":"06c896d0e7e0cdde5ef1825cb27fe58af3a97017","tid":195204,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:28:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實青山教係玩分身<br />\n<br />\n一人整十數個專頁, 扮多人<br />\n<br />\n事實係連街站都開唔到一個</blockquote><br />\n少年，你太年輕了。你以為這個熱狗真的有那麼多古人支持？其實都是我一個人開的，不然我再換個古人發同樣的話給你看。"},{"pid":"219fc4df1fbf0cc3b1cac7e7cd67f77602a4ccc4","tid":195204,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:45:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e650392346a49e4f775cba1511cf1976fbfaa09","tid":195204,"uid":67813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:12:17.000Z","msg":"Diu,如果真係甘多支持者就唔會得一個入到啦"},{"pid":"f94fd6f8627f1008535ad9d74769ffa5508b49cb","tid":195204,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:22:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實青山教係玩分身<br />\n<br />\n一人整十數個專頁, 扮多人<br />\n<br />\n事實係連街站都開唔到一個</blockquote><br />\n青山教派多廢青，可以日日24小時上網打飛機， 營造左一個人多勢衆既幼覺.......一去到現實世界就現形</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係因為青山教派係用宗教方式、個人崇拜去傳播<br />\n而熱狗則係幫會式既發展, 亦係完全既個人崇拜<br />\n所以佢地有呢種特質<br />\n<br />\n獨派遲早都需要咁做<br />\n只係獨派現時仍然係論述傳播階段, 所以仲未以幫會式既做法去做<br />\n論述傳播係一個必經而重要既階段黎, 不可skip<br />\n你無呢個階段, 就會好似熱狗咁, 完全被青山教派附身, <br />\n思想操控左<br />\n<br />\n獨派既論述發展, 不單對抗大中華思想, 更加係打擊陳云根既思想操控<br />\n所以搞到云伯咁憎獨派"},{"pid":"eef5109c95eae901cc2f88fb3efc78df4a232bea","tid":195204,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:38:17.000Z","msg":"絕對服從首領，如果熱普城有guts，將會無好犀利嘅軍團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可惜無<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40379980e18cdff69182525823d2ed44186fa6b6","tid":195204,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:50:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絕對服從首領，如果熱普城有guts，將會無好犀利嘅軍團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜無<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為首領無GUTS <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"730dab7fced77620947c09a0a6b78763bea64072","tid":195204,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:55:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>絕對服從首領，如果熱普城有guts，將會無好犀利嘅軍團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜無<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為首領無GUTS <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n口講勇武"},{"pid":"8351d6d76662559af71bf50f3ecd0605f97e05eb","tid":195204,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T03:36:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>絕對服從首領，如果熱普城有guts，將會無好犀利嘅軍團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜無<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為首領無GUTS <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n口講勇武</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食新鮮洪瑞珍方面, 極之勇武咬落去"},{"pid":"faa404428718e5bdb4265c04dc9abe7ec5d0c497","tid":195204,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T09:12:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>絕對服從首領，如果熱普城有guts，將會無好犀利嘅軍團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜無<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為首領無GUTS <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n口講勇武</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食新鮮洪瑞珍方面, 極之勇武咬落去</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da154efe8148d1211cccb406265c29e3d2afb2b","tid":195204,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:26:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}